Package: VARim
Title: Time series imputation using VAR-IM
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Muhammad Edy", "Rizal", , "edyrizalmuh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-7407-1059"))
Description: VARim imputes missing data in multivariate time series data based on Vector Autoregression Imputation Method (VAR-IM). The package can also be used for data with seasonality.
